<%# Impact Beyond Us principle page template - content to be added %>
<div class="principle-page impact-beyond-us">
  <%# Meta tags %>
  <% content_for :title, "Building Tomorrow's Professional Services - Wrantle" %>
  <% content_for :meta_description, "Discover how Wrantle is elevating professional services across emerging markets through structured development, market enhancement, and innovative integration." %>
  <% content_for :meta_keywords, "professional excellence, emerging markets, capability development, service innovation, market enhancement, professional services" %>
  <% content_for :og_title, "Building Tomorrow's Professional Services - Wrantle" %>
  <% content_for :og_description, "Discover how Wrantle is elevating professional services across emerging markets through structured development, market enhancement, and innovative integration." %>

  <%# About Navigation %>
  <%= render "shared/about_navigation" %>

  <%# Hero Section %>
  <%= render(Primer::Box.new(mt: 6, p: 4, classes: "principle-hero")) do %>
    <div class="service-icon ripple-effect">
      <%= render "shared/impact_icon" %>
    </div>
    <%= render(Primer::Beta::Heading.new(tag: :h1, font_weight: :bold)) { "Impact Beyond Us" } %>
    <%= render(Primer::Beta::Text.new(tag: :h2, classes: "hero-subheading")) { "Building Tomorrow's Professional Excellence" } %>
  <% end %>

  <%# Content Section %>
  <%= render(Primer::Box.new(p: 4, classes: "principle-content")) do %>
    <%= render(Primer::Beta::Text.new(tag: :p, classes: "principle-text")) do %>
      At Wrantle, our vision extends to actively developing future talents for emerging markets.
    <% end %>

    <%= render(Primer::Beta::Heading.new(tag: :h2, mb: 2)) { "Development Platform" } %>
    <%= render(Primer::Beta::Text.new(tag: :p, classes: "principle-text")) do %>
      We've built a structured system for developing high-caliber professionals. This combines practical experience with targeted training across key service areas - from complex corporate structuring to innovative financial solutions. Our systematic approach ensures consistent delivery while building lasting professional capabilities.
    <% end %>

    <%= render(Primer::Beta::Heading.new(tag: :h2, mb: 2)) { "Market Enhancement" } %>
    <%= render(Primer::Beta::Text.new(tag: :p, classes: "principle-text")) do %>
      We address a critical need in emerging markets - the development of world-class professional service capabilities. Our focused development program creates professionals who combine deep local market understanding with international service standards.
    <% end %>

    <%= render(Primer::Beta::Heading.new(tag: :h2, mb: 2)) { "Innovation Integration" } %>
    <%= render(Primer::Beta::Text.new(tag: :p, classes: "principle-text")) do %>
      Our development approach emphasizes modern service delivery. We integrate current technologies and innovative practices into our work, ensuring our professionals stay ahead of market developments. This forward-looking stance enables more efficient, effective solutions for complex business challenges.
    <% end %>

    <%= render(Primer::Beta::Heading.new(tag: :h2, mb: 2)) { "Future Focus" } %>
    <%= render(Primer::Beta::Text.new(tag: :p, classes: "principle-text")) do %>
      By investing in capability development today, we build capacity for tomorrow's professional service needs. Our commitment extends beyond immediate requirements to creating lasting positive change in professional service delivery across emerging markets.
    <% end %>

    <%= render(Primer::Beta::Text.new(tag: :p, classes: "principle-text")) do %>
      This focused development directly strengthens your business through access to consistently high-quality professional services, delivered by well-trained experts who understand both local and international business contexts.
    <% end %>
  <% end %>

  <%# Contact Section %>
  <%= render "shared/contact_box",
    title: "Ready to experience world-class service?",
    subtitle: "Let's discuss how our expertise can drive your success" %>
</div>
